text: Tako Adamia () is a Georgian beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned and placed as the first runner-up of Miss Georgia 2018. She will now represent Georgia at the Miss Universe 2019 competition. == Pageantry == Adamia began her pageantry career as she competed at Miss Georgia 2018. She was crowned as the first runner-up to Nini Gogichaishvili, she succeeded outgoing titleholder Lara Yan. == References == Category:Miss Universe 2019 contestants Category:1990s births Category:Living people
